                        </div>
                        <br />
                        <div class="social d-flex text-center">
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sefa-a%C5%9Fik-35a9b921a/" class="px-2 py-2 mr-md-1 rounded"><span class="ion-logo-facebook mr-2"></span> Linkedİn</a>
                            <a href="https://sefaasik.com/" class="px-2 py-2 ml-md-1 rounded"><span class="ion-logo-twitter mr-2"></span> sefaasik.com</a>
